data.description: Come see this beautiful spacious Tri-level with 3 bedrooms 2 baths. This home features a bright large living room with vaulted ceilings, dining area, large family or recreational room. Laundry room with new washer and dryer included. Can't miss the charming updated kitchen with stainless steel appliances all staying with the home. Home has a huge backyard with driveway parking for a few vehicles.    Call and schedule showing today!
